      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">53.204-1</ph> Safeguarding classified
information within industry (DDForm254, DDForm441).</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3801e8" rev="FAC 2020-07 August 3, 2020" class="- topic/p "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2015-002?>The
following forms, which are prescribed by the Department of Defense,
shall be used by DoD components and those nondefense agencies with
which DoD has agreements to provide industrial security services
for the National Industrial Security Program if contractor access
to classified information is required, as specified in subpart  <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="FAR_Subpart_4_4"
                  href="Subpart_4.4.dita#FAR_Subpart_4_4">4.4</xref> and the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="FAR_52_204_2"
                  href="52.204-2.dita#FAR_52_204_2">52.204-2</xref>:<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 53.204-1 by revising the introductory text.?></p>
         <ol id="d3766e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3801e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">DD Form 254(Department
of Defense (DoD)), Contract Security Classification Specification</i>.
(See <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "
                        base="FAR_4_403"
                        href="4.403.dita#FAR_4_403">4.403</xref>(c)(1).)</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3801e30" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">DD Form 441(DoD),
Security Agreement</i>. (See paragraph (b) of the clause at <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref "
                        base="FAR_52_204_2"
                        href="52.204-2.dita#FAR_52_204_2">52.204-2</xref>.)</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
